00:16:15.279 --> 00:16:16.806
- [Reporter] Is it worth
coming all the way?

355
00:16:16.841 --> 00:16:18.049
- Absolutely.

356
00:16:18.084 --> 00:16:19.116
If you're passionate
about your team.

357
00:16:19.151 --> 00:16:20.711
you follow them
wherever they are.

358
00:16:20.746 --> 00:16:22.119
- [Reporter] With the clock
ticking down to kick off.

359
00:16:22.154 --> 00:16:25.155
the excitement continues
to rise here in Barcelona.

360
00:16:25.190 --> 00:16:27.322
Wherever you go. there's
a sea of fans who seem

361
00:16:27.357 --> 00:16:30.193
to have taken over the
city ahead of the final.

