00:16:40.205 --> 00:16:42.029
- Fantastic. Absolutely superb.

367
00:16:42.064 --> 00:16:43.437
- [Reporter] Yeah.
- It's a joy to be here.

368
00:16:43.472 --> 00:16:45.439
- I mean. the atmosphere
alone is worth coming for.

