00:16:45.474 --> 00:16:46.605
It's superb.

370
00:16:46.640 --> 00:16:48.211
The weather and
everything. It's great.

371
00:16:48.246 --> 00:16:51.148
- Soaking up the atmosphere
in Barcelona. aren't you?

