00:17:06.957 --> 00:17:09.496
United set off to
Barcelona with the hopes

381
00:17:09.531 --> 00:17:11.234
of doing the unimaginable.

382
00:17:11.269 --> 00:17:14.270
Dreaming of once again
bringing the European Cup

383
00:17:14.305 --> 00:17:15.832
back to old Trafford.

