00:19:49.427 --> 00:19:51.295
He fell in love with Victoria.

431
00:19:51.330 --> 00:19:53.792
That changed
everything. I think.

432
00:19:53.827 --> 00:19:56.531
Well. it was a different
type of marriage

433
00:19:56.566 --> 00:19:58.830
from what you would
normally expect

434
00:20:00.097 --> 00:20:01.635
