winning the war for territory.

1463
01:04:20.722 --> 01:04:24.031
Cape Town is decked
out in red and white.

1464
01:04:24.066 --> 01:04:25.593
- You got to get there early.

1465
01:04:25.628 --> 01:04:27.100
We're flying anoraks. so
you got to get there early.

1466
01:04:27.135 --> 01:04:30.070
get the flag up. otherwise
you lose all the best spaces.

1467
01:04:31.502 --> 01:04:33.436
- [Reporter] The world's
biggest England shirt

1468
01:04:33.471 --> 01:04:34.976
has even made it here.

1469
01:04:35.011 --> 01:04:38.507
a sign of the huge
expectations that 2010

1470
01:04:38.542 --> 01:04:40.608
will live up to the past.

1471
01:04:40.643 --> 01:04:42.115
- We're at our best when
our backs are to the wall.

1472
01:04:42.150 --> 01:04:44.051
and I think the
lads will make sure

1473
01:04:44.086 --> 01:04:46.317
that they rub a few noses
in it after this one.

1474
01:04:46.352 --> 01:04:49.056
- [Reporter] They know
this is make or break time

1475
01:04:49.091 --> 01:04:51.685
for England. but they're
convinced the team

1476
01:04:51.720 --> 01:04:54.996
will light up the Cape
Town stadium tonight.

1477
01:04:57.726 --> 01:05:00.133
(tense music)

1478
01:05:16.976 --> 01:05:19.416
- [Narrator] On the
14th of March. 2010.

1479
01:05:19.451 --> 01:05:22.089
Beckham's dreams at a World
Cup comeback were shattered

1480
01:05:22.124 --> 01:05:24.718
after he suffered a torn
left Achilles tendon.

1481
01:05:24.753 --> 01:05:27.127
playing against the
Kievo in Serie A.

1482
01:05:28.592 --> 01:05:31.593
Unbeknownst to him. Beckham
had played his last game

1483
01:05:31.628 --> 01:05:33.892
in the famous
three lions Jersey.

1484
01:05:33.927 --> 01:05:35.366
- I know the country
is in mourning.

1485
01:05:35.401 --> 01:05:37.731
I think mainly because
everyone admires David Beckham

1486
01:05:37.766 --> 01:05:40.239
as a person. and for what he's
done for England in the past.

1487
01:05:40.274 --> 01:05:42.010
- You obviously need
the experienced players

1488
01:05:42.045 --> 01:05:44.210
to boost the younger players.

1489
01:05:44.245 --> 01:05:46.179
So missing out on David Beckham.

1490
01:05:46.214 --> 01:05:48.247
it would probably
be a bit of a shame.

1491
01:05:48.282 --> 01:05:51.118
- I'm so sorry for here for him.

1492
01:05:51.153 --> 01:05:56.156
because I know how
he wanted to go.

1493
01:05:58.391 --> 01:06:00.688
And the workup. he went.

1494
01:06:00.723 --> 01:06:05.660
He came last year in
Milan. above all for this.

1495
01:06:06.861 --> 01:06:10.434
to show his quality
for the England team.

1496
01:06:10.469 --> 01:06:12.238
I'm so sorry for this.

1497
01:06:12.273 --> 01:06:15.175
- [Narrator] After a brief
six month spell at PSG.

1498
01:06:15.210 --> 01:06:17.606
the day finally came
to hang up the boots.

1499
01:06:17.641 --> 01:06:20.004
and public opinion
was ever contrasting

1500
01:06:20.039 --> 01:06:21.412
to that of 1998.

1501
01:06:21.447 --> 01:06:23.447
- I think that was
right moment to stop.

1502
01:06:24.747 --> 01:06:26.351
You have to expect this.

1503
01:06:26.386 --> 01:06:30.322
Of course. not just PSG.

1504
01:06:30.357 --> 01:06:34.887
but the football world
lost a fantastic player.

1505
01:06:34.922 --> 01:06:39.925
Lost a fantastic professional
player. Lost a good man.

1506
01:06:41.170 --> 01:06:42.532
- Well. it's a sad day.

1507
01:06:42.567 --> 01:06:45.733
I can imagine that there are
many boys. men and women.

1508
01:06:45.768 --> 01:06:49.176
all over the world that
are mourning the loss

1509
01:06:49.211 --> 01:06:50.375
of a football star.

1510
01:06:50.410 --> 01:06:52.245
He's an absolute icon.

1511
01:06:52.280 --> 01:06:54.346
- Beckham was out
of order. basically.

1512
01:06:54.381 --> 01:06:55.446
He should have
stayed on the field.

1513
01:06:55.481 --> 01:06:57.250
and if he had have done.
we'd have got through.

1514
01:06:57.285 --> 01:07:00.121
- Professional footballer
committed to the cause.

1515
01:07:00.156 --> 01:07:01.782
loved the clubs
that he played for.

1516
01:07:03.016 --> 01:07:05.489
Today. footballers. you
know. you could question

1517
01:07:05.524 --> 01:07:06.952
some of their motivations.

1518
01:07:06.987 --> 01:07:09.361
You never had your
questions about him

1519
01:07:09.396 --> 01:07:10.890
and his motivations at all.

1520
01:07:10.925 --> 01:07:12.364
- To get sent off
in a match like that

1521
01:07:12.399 --> 01:07:14.333
is a disgrace to anybody.

1522
01:07:14.368 --> 01:07:15.466
I'm sorry for his career.

1523
01:07:18.471 --> 01:07:21.065
- Say. for football in England.

1524
01:07:21.100 --> 01:07:23.210
So he'll continue his
role as an ambassador.

1525
01:07:23.245 --> 01:07:25.410
I know he's in a lot of
work in the Far East.

1526
01:07:25.445 --> 01:07:28.479
in his training roles. you
know. for kids and stuff.

1527
01:07:28.514 --> 01:07:30.415
So he'll still be around.

1528
01:07:30.450 --> 01:07:32.516
He'll be around for a long
time. forever. you know?

1529
01:07:32.551 --> 01:07:35.090
Till he's well old. So
you never lose them.

1530
01:07:35.950 --> 01:07:38.951
(children shouting)

1531
01:07:46.466 --> 01:07:48.026
- [Alex] He's become fantastic.

1532
01:07:48.061 --> 01:07:51.062
How can I argue with how he's
turned out as a human being?

1533
01:07:51.097 --> 01:07:53.240
He's an icon to every
kid in the world.

1534
01:07:53.275 --> 01:07:55.176
he's a very wealthy guy.

1535
01:07:55.211 --> 01:07:57.112
So how can I possibly
argue with that?

1536
01:08:01.943 --> 01:08:05.153
- [Narrator] Amid the fame.
red carpets and brand deals.

1537
01:08:05.188 --> 01:08:07.584
Beckham pioneered
a fresh new look

1538
01:08:07.619 --> 01:08:10.356
of what a modern
day footballer is.

1539
01:08:11.887 --> 01:08:13.953
With the odds
stacked against him.

1540
01:08:13.988 --> 01:08:16.087
the young boy from
Leytonstone went on

1541
01:08:16.122 --> 01:08:18.430
to win a long list
of silverware.

1542
01:08:18.465 --> 01:08:21.400
including six PL
titles. two FA cups.

1543
01:08:21.435 --> 01:08:23.963
one La Liga. one
Champions League.

1544
01:08:23.998 --> 01:08:26.504
and one PFA Young
Player of the Year.

1545
01:08:28.409 --> 01:08:31.509
He conquered England.
Italy and America.

1546
01:08:31.544 --> 01:08:34.446
both commercially
and as an athlete.

1547
01:08:34.481 --> 01:08:38.043
became the third highest capped
English player of all time.

1548
01:08:38.078 --> 01:08:42.289
and smashed shirt sale records
at Madrid and LA Galaxy.

1549
01:08:42.324 --> 01:08:45.952
whilst also becoming the
highest paid player of all time.

1550
01:08:49.364 --> 01:08:51.529
There is no doubting
the financial success

1551
01:08:51.564 --> 01:08:52.860
of Beckham's career.

1552
01:08:56.503 --> 01:08:59.438
And when a player wins as
many trophies as Becks.

1553
01:08:59.473 --> 01:09:01.737
there's no doubting their
playing career either.

1554
01:09:03.477 --> 01:09:06.346
(gentle piano music)

1555
01:09:19.086 --> 01:09:19.986
- [Reporter] Back
home in England

1556
01:09:20.021 --> 01:09:21.691
as the excitement builds.

1557
01:09:21.726 --> 01:09:24.188
one 10-year-old by has
taken his love of the game

1558
01:09:24.223 --> 01:09:25.596
a little too far.

1559
01:09:25.631 --> 01:09:29.061
Tom Sylvester chose to
go bald before his years.

1560
01:09:29.096 --> 01:09:31.470
to look like his hero. Sven.

1561
01:09:31.505 --> 01:09:33.164
- There's quite a lot
of people in the school

1562
01:09:33.199 --> 01:09:34.374
who dress up as David Beckham.

1563
01:09:34.409 --> 01:09:37.135
and I thought Sven
would be different.

1564
01:09:38.413 --> 01:09:40.479
Because when I
first had it done.

1565
01:09:40.514 --> 01:09:43.416
it was almost bald. and I fought
everyone would laugh at me.

1566
01:09:43.451 --> 01:09:44.417
But they haven't. They've
started liking it.



